profile:
I am a 24 year old male, who just recently started his own company. The last 6 years I have built custom homes from the ground up. I am a general contractor now, who can and would love any type of work in the field of carpentry or construction. I have my redseal as a carpenter and have the skill level and requirements to complete many different types of construction work. I was a supervisor at RWH construction, Custom homes and cottages, and ran the concrete crew for my last couple years working for them. I am excellent at installing trim, tile, any finish work and custom based work, I also have done a lot of timber work, and siding, landscape, I can run excavators and machinery, I can also construct decks, any type of concrete, framing, etc. 

If you are in need of a job done, it would be my honour to help achieve your goals. I look forward to hearing from anyone about any type of job. Please contact me by email or by my cell and weâ€™ll arrange a meet and greet and get a quote and time frame made up around my cheaper than the rest base rates and pricing ! Thank-you, I look forward to future greetings !
